snippet.title: Gradius Universe Ver 1.05 R.Option Very Hard Loop 20
snippet.description:
Going through this really good Gradius fangame called Universe. The v1.05 update added R.Options. So far my favorite is F.Options, R.Option hurts my eyes during boss fights which caused a few deaths. 
You can get the game here:
http://www.esc-j.net/stg/stgdu/upload.php
It'll usually be called STG【UNIVERSE】ver###
